name: GENOCIDA
description:
## SOUND ON ##

September 7th, 2021 - Brazil is a democratic nation and will still be, even if some bads seed try to destroy it! 

A "tribute" to Bolsonaro, President of Brazil, and all his genocidal actions before and during the pandemic. 

All sounds of this song comes from the autor voice, recorded on ZOOM H4N and worked on Ableton Live. 
Composed by Gabriel Politzer; sound artist, musician and biologist from Rio de Janeiro.

Genres: critic, eletronic
Release Date: April 1, 2021
